{
  "stem": "13981.3",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I thought I was going-- I had hoped I was going to be an interpreter, but I was made a translator.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I tried it out for interpreter once, but I didn't cut the mustard.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] It's a very difficult thing to hear one language over the earphone, and speak simultaneously into a microphone in another language.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I, I didn't qualify.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But a funny incident again, one of the interpreters there was a person who had been born in White Russia.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And somehow gotten out of Russia and had lived in England.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he was one of those people that knew just about every European language that needed to be known.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He spoke English, Russian, of course, Spanish, Italian, German.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I think a few-- think-- a few other Slavic languages thrown in.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Anyhow, the interpreters only worked every other day.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "On their off day, they took a practice session during the court's lunch hour.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They were given difficult legal terms to practice.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "In other words, somebody told them something and they had to get it in.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And on this particular day, this person, while talking, while listening Russian, talking English, a friend of his gave him a note written in French.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And while working those two languages in his mind, he answered in writing in French.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "It's phenomenal.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Really phenomenal.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was assigned to a translating section.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the person in charge there at that time, if I remember right, was Lieutenant [?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Niebergall ?], [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] who has since died, but whose wife I met in Wash-- these-- and whose sister-in-law was another secretary lives here in town, Mrs.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Ivy.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And well, they put us to work getting us acquainted.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
